Rating: 4
This is my number 1 summer dessert. Everyone loves it. As recommended by another reviewer, I do mix extra gingersnap crumbs to sprinkle over the top before serving and I have found Anna's Ginger Thins (available at Walgreen's) the best I've tried as they are very thin and crispy.

