Rating: 4
The gingersnap crust was a huge hit, and the lemon was just lemony enough. I would suggest making some extra crust and scattering that over the top of the pie, as there was so much fighting over extra crust! Also, not necessary to have an ice cream maker-- go to the following website (it's a science website) for an easy way to make ice cream with just ziploc bags, ice, and salt! http://sci-toys.com/scitoys/scitoys/thermo/ice_cream/ice_cream.html

